nodes.text: A Chiss Ruling Family was active on the isolated colony world Schesa, located along the Way of Schesa, a hyperlane. It fell on the losing side of a civil war before the Swarm War.
This unidentified family was first mentioned on page 223 of The Essential Atlas, in the collective description of the planets Catlia, Massoss, Sharb, Noris, Schesa and Ornfra.
